{"tid":2114444,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"反串女鬼死於8964後  志雲網劇 唔怕踩中國安法","createTime":"2020-07-18T20:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T07:56:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8c80b895768b623a68a025eb2b95c64313c41b","tid":2114444,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T20:51:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200718/FK7WUNV43MM5T5DPFNMLHN4XEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200718%2FFK7WUNV43MM5T5DPFNMLHN4XEU%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=2b9261f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200718%2FFK7WUNV43MM5T5DPFNMLHN4XEU%2F&h=192fe813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200718/FK7WUNV43MM5T5DPFNMLHN4XEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n反串女鬼死於8964後 <br />\n志雲網劇 唔怕踩中國安法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲除了頻道節目，近日又有新搞作，將與石詠莉、莫竣名（Louis）和劉亭君（Ivy）等合演處境網劇《姨媽到》，他會反串飾演女鬼Margaret Elizabeth Dunn，不過此處境劇涉及「八九六四」、「慘死」、「冤魂」等內容，隨時有機會觸犯早前生效的港區國安法，志雲聞言笑說：「我係鬼嚟㗎，點會踩界啫，一啲界都冇踩。喺社會大環境之下，你會知道我哋好貼地，但說話同劇情發展，叫人去示威、分裂國家、叛逆，呢啲意識係冇嘅，我哋唔推廣嘅。只係佢哋劇中間咖啡店展示咗啲相，係香港發生過嘅嘢，記者影嗰啲相。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：甩底避鋒頭 梁漢文個唱延期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n志雲新搞作處境劇《姨媽到》會涉及「八九六四」、「慘死」、「冤魂」等內容。<br />\n逗港人開心<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。因此一叫「姨媽到」便立即現身。而Louis指新劇內容主要講疫情，他強調：「我哋連口號都冇嘅。」港台《頭條新聞》受打壓已於上月停播，現推出《姨媽到》是否有意接棒？Ivy否認說：「個疫情一開始我哋就計劃，諗啲嘢等香港人開心吓。」志雲笑說：「受疫情影響啲話劇演員邊有得開工箒？如果冇得開工，我咪可以剝削佢哋，叫佢哋收平啲做。志雲投資，佢儍㗎，明明冇回報，不過你老闆（黎智英）嗰種儍仲危險，隨時俾人拉，我呢種最多蝕晒箒。」<br />\n<br />\n近日傳出內地廣電局再新增20條禁令，包括愛情戲不能太甜蜜、穿越題材要有「合理科學解釋」及同性戀題材要轉為友情。。。。。。。。。。。。。摩到令到佢冇咁城市化，同理兄弟之間唔可以相殘，惡人一定要受到懲罰。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UCajKKaNER27rFgz6zRER4wuPws=/640x350/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N2OZU22N7LN44JJS6YTGXCWYKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUCajKKaNER27rFgz6zRER4wuPws%3D%2F640x350%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN2OZU22N7LN44JJS6YTGXCWYKM.jpg&h=5c70a2f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉亭君被志雲上身後，與初戀情人「曾俊華」講數。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MvzSeG2Q9-Jn7UtitVU1MVkMSms=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FX4FJMDLQ7CJBK4LIZ2CXXJNDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMvzSeG2Q9-Jn7UtitVU1MVkMSms%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFX4FJMDLQ7CJBK4LIZ2CXXJNDE.jpg&h=9dc2a99e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首次反串演女鬼的陳志雲，鬼魂寄存在一個咖啡壺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S7PzF0AmjX2wHT_sM2j5nk4390Q=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/COZQFDGWE3WECC6SIRHIEXMU44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS7PzF0AmjX2wHT_sM2j5nk4390Q%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCOZQFDGWE3WECC6SIRHIEXMU44.jpg&h=cdeb6edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫竣名（右）和劉亭君都指新劇是講述疫情，並強調「連口號都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬧無綫加辣<br />\n<br />\n無綫對藝人合約也傳加辣，。。。。。。。。。。。。暫定七集的《姨媽到》將於本月27日王喜53歲生日及志雲母親死忌當天，在志雲YouTube頻道播出。"},{"pid":"507c0f50e317c047aeec8899bef8f33d598a211d","tid":2114444,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T01:46:20.000Z","msg":"有mcm <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59a6b8172c1137e7efe9ab41a2efce900c7df34","tid":2114444,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"將與石詠莉、莫竣名（Louis）和劉亭君（Ivy）等合演處境網劇《姨媽到》"}]}